snippet.title: Frog Fighters Trailer
snippet.description:
Frog Fighters is a light-hearted, fast-paced, third-person-shooter where you become a frog on a lily pad with an ability to shoot other flying frogs with different types of laser-leafs.

Steam Page:
Discord: https://discord.gg/EtAUpNnBbF
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Frog_Fighters
